branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VQC series has five standard wiring packages bringing a world of ease to wiring and maintenance work, while the protective enclosures of three of them conform to IP67 standards for protection from dust and moisture. The use of multi-pin connectors to replace wiring inside manifold blocks provides flexibility when adding stations or changing manifold configuration. The VQC series has outstanding response times and long life.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Normally open or normally closed available&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compact and large flow capacity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Metal seal type available with high voltage function&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rubber seal type available with dual 3-port valves, 4 positions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

